  "prompt": "What are some toy manufacturers in Mexico?",
  "response": "Mexico has a vibrant toy manufacturing industry with several notable companies. Here are a few toy manufacturers based in Mexico:\n\n1. **Juguetes Mi Alegr\u00eda** - Known for educational and scientific toys, they produce toy kits that encourage learning and creativity among children.\n\n2. **Lego Operaciones de M\u00e9xico** - While not originally a Mexican company, LEGO has significant manufacturing operations in Mexico, contributing to the local toy production industry.\n\n3. **Fotorama de M\u00e9xico** - They offer a wide range of toys including games and activity sets, known for their innovative and creative designs.\n\n4. **Montables y Juegos Infantiles, S.A. de C.V.** - Specializes in ride-on toys and playground equipment, both for home and commercial use.\n\nThese companies, among others, contribute significantly to the toy industry in Mexico, offering a variety of products ranging from educational toys to games and outdoor play equipment.",
